    <summary>Slope based vegetation indices.

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Difference Vegetation Index
    DVI = NIR - R&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Normalized Difference Vegetation Index (Rouse et al. 1974)
    NDVI = (NIR - R) / (NIR + R)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ratio Vegetation Index (Richardson and Wiegand, 1977)
    RVI = R / NIR&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Normalized Ratio Vegetation Index (Baret and Guyot, 1991)
    NRVI = (RVI - 1) / (RVI + 1)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transformed Vegetation Index (Deering et al., 1975)
    TVI = [(NIR - R) / (NIR + R) + 0.5]^0.5&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Corrected Transformed Ratio Vegetation Index (Perry and Lautenschlager, 1984)
    CTVI = [(NDVI + 0.5) / abs(NDVI + 0.5)] * [abs(NDVI + 0.5)]^0.5&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thiam's Transformed Vegetation Index (Thiam, 1997)
    RVI = [abs(NDVI) + 0.5]^0.5&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Soil Adjusted Vegetation Index (Huete, 1988)
    SAVI = [(NIR - R) / (NIR + R + L)] * (1 + L)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;(NIR = near infrared, R = red, S = soil adjustment factor)


</summary>
